  str(e) exposed.
- GET /welcome -> checks 'user_id' in request.session, redirects to 
  /login if missing. Reads dashboard.html from disk, does 
  html.replace('{{username}}', username), returns HTMLResponse 
  (vulnerability #2 -- stored XSS)
- GET /logout -> request.session.clear(), RedirectResponse to /login

